:TPS603–TPS603.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1200/JCO.2019.37.15_suppl.TPS603">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=The+international+collaboration+of+active+surveillance+trials+for+low-risk+DCIS+%28LORIS%2C+LORD%2C+COMET%2C+LORETTA%29&amp;author=C+Kanbayashi&amp;author=AM+Thompson&amp;author=ESS+Hwang&amp;publication_year=2019&amp;journal=J+Clin+Oncol&amp;doi=10.1200%2FJCO.2019.37.15_suppl.TPS603">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Tabár L, Vitak B, Chen TH, et al. Swedish two-county trial: impact of mammographic screening on breast cancer mortality during 3 decades. <em>Radiology</em> 2011;260(3):658–663.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/radiol.11110469">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21712474/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Swedish+two-county+trial%3A+impact+of+mammographic+screening+on+breast+cancer+mortality+during+3+decades&amp;author=L+Tab%C3%A1r&amp;author=B+Vitak&amp;author=TH+Chen&amp;publication_year=2011&amp;journal=Radiology&amp;pages=658-663&amp;doi=10.1148%2Fradiol.11110469&amp;pmid=21712474">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Siegel RL, Miller KD, Jemal A. Cancer statistics, 2019. <em>CA Cancer J Clin 2019</em>;69(1):7–34.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.3322/caac.21551">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="htt